One of the most popular BBNaija housemates and rapper, Laycon has clocked 1Million followers on Instagram, becoming the first and presently, the only housemate to hit one million followers on any social platform. <img src="https://i1.wp.com/notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/laycon-afeo-1-640x389.png?resize=640%2C389&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1"/> This is a huge feat for the rapper who came into the house, not as popular with just 3715 followers has now hit one million with verified status both on Instagram and Twitter. <img src="https://i1.wp.com/notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Screenshot_20200919-205836_WhatsApp-357x420.jpg?resize=357%2C420&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1"/>
